  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      It should be known by the clinician that COVID-19 patients are prone to anxiety, and these&#xD;
      disorders need to be properly diagnosed and addressed to improve prognosis, shorten hospital&#xD;
      stay and avoid long-term mental health problems.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
